org.apache.calcite.rel.core

类 TableFunctionScan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.AbstractRelNode
      • org.apache.calcite.rel.core.TableFunctionScan
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Cloneable, RelOptNode, RelNode
    直接已知子类:
    EnumerableTableFunctionScan, LogicalTableFunctionScan

    public abstract class TableFunctionScan
extends AbstractRelNode
    Relational expression that calls a table-valued function.

    The function returns a result set. It can appear as a leaf in a query tree, or can be applied to relational inputs.

    另请参阅:
    LogicalTableFunctionScan

      • getChildExps

        public List<RexNode> getChildExps()
        从接口复制的说明: RelNode
        Returns a list of this relational expression's child expressions. (These are scalar expressions, and so do not include the relational inputs that are returned by RelNode.getInputs().

        The caller should treat the list as unmodifiable; typical implementations will return an immutable list. If there are no child expressions, returns an empty list, not null.

        指定者:
        getChildExps 在接口中 RelNode
        覆盖:
